Old Testament
The Old Testament includes 39 books which were written long before Jesus was born.




The Old Testament books are divided into five groups 
(find out more):

Torah (Law of Moses):
        Genesis
         Exodus
      Leviticus
        Numbers
    Deuteronomy


Historical Writings:
         Joshua
         Judges
           Ruth
        1 Samuel
        2 Samuel
         1 Kings
         2 Kings
    1 Chronicles
    2 Chronicles
           Ezra
       Nehemiah
         Esther


Wisdom and Poetry:
            Job
         Psalms
       Proverbs
   Ecclesiastes
  Song of Solomon


Major Prophets:
